{"tid":1227134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］中學生忍夠了 暫你老母","createTime":"2019-06-15T14:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T02:13:01.000Z","uid":25001,"like":1713,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"797d4ecb9532c94a1699aa9ffb3a9b3452229938","tid":1227134,"uid":25001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:34:01.000Z","msg":"阻你一陣<br />\n<br />\n我們連續幾天的抗爭仍未得到正當回應<br />\n警察和政府的不合理對待使全世界嘩然<br />\n但即使採用任何手段 也不能令香港人滅聲<br />\n香港全民歸位<br />\n不甘示弱 只為明天<br />\n6.16 不見不散<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以用少少時間睇段片 我地中學生用左一晚時間剪片<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Share 出去<br />\n我地一日不撤回 一日不散去<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rpjIPEuHtLw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrpjIPEuHtLw&d=1pbl5WvK8XMTdm%2FDcZs%2FeHljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=077d40dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rpjIPEuHtLw</a>"},{"pid":"b7dff85a19a4ddc7963083235c0a917d6e055b49","tid":1227134,"uid":84068,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:34:39.000Z","msg":"推了訓身支持"},{"pid":"84e0e5054433c8e1f9b232705a6b2683e638ef63","tid":1227134,"uid":241545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:34:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3529998333987be918850da56acc40bad713f83a","tid":1227134,"uid":25001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:35:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5dbb945b0b91e1ea5241d7c77eb9df15bfba86eb","tid":1227134,"uid":25001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:35:27.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7024f1cd0b733dfbe3623f3bb5bca8518569b50e","tid":1227134,"uid":25001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:35:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598246b85cf60b37464d63ee4466da6c040de0b3","tid":1227134,"uid":73619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:36:19.000Z","msg":"想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46bd38a3d5dcd765310aa14ad9655d3da1266cfe","tid":1227134,"uid":178418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:36:31.000Z","msg":"push!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a340ac9607dc362eb69c3c521d968eefae59271","tid":1227134,"uid":77321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:36:33.000Z","msg":"Thank you for your hard work<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f242a3744867fe3156764f01cafc664d6f7188","tid":1227134,"uid":123050,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:36:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>行政機關濫用權力之審判</strong></span><br />\n二戰末期，納粹德國敗局已現，佛斯曼醫師、門格勒、拉舍爾三人的命運也隨著戰爭快速流轉。1945年時，拉舍爾因犯罪而被處死，和被他殺死的許多人一樣，葬身於達豪集中營裡。而門格勒假扮成一般士兵，躲過追緝後流亡到南美洲，直到1979年在巴西意外溺斃後才被確認身分。而始終堅持人性的佛斯曼醫師則在戰火中存活了下來，1945年時游過易北河後向美軍投降，戰後以泌尿科醫師的身份默默地生活著。在惡魔的年代結束之際，三名醫師分別擁來了他們各自的結局&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/5bd929a85b8a970c9c8fd7567b295223-e1450778342448.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpansci.asia%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F12%2F5bd929a85b8a970c9c8fd7567b295223-e1450778342448.jpg&h=327c7f1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左上圖：將人浸入冰水當中，藉此研究在低溫下人體的反應；左下圖：故意讓小孩感染結核菌，並切除腋下的淋巴腺，測試人體的免疫力；右圖：紐倫堡審判中，對卡爾&middot;勃蘭特（Karl Brandt）醫師的審判，他被控同意並參與非人道實驗和其他戰爭罪行，最後被判絞刑。<br />\n用屍體換來的規範－紐倫堡守則<br />\n堆積如山的屍體、骨瘦如柴的幸存者，那些泯滅人性的實驗震撼了全世界。1948年在紐倫堡進行的醫師審判，被告的醫師之中，不乏知名的科學家，如施靈（Klaus Karl Schilling）曾是國際瘧疾研究聯盟的成員，戰時卻刻意讓一千多名囚犯感染瘧疾來進行科學研究。科學家在戰爭期間荒唐的行徑，讓美國醫師里昂&middot;亞歷山大（Leo Alexander）動筆起草人體實驗中應有的道德規範，也就是今日我們熟知的「紐倫堡公約」，寫明了醫師在任何情況之下，都不得傷害受試者（除非受試者就是醫師本人）。而1964年在芬蘭舉辦的全球醫師大會更提出「赫爾辛基宣言（The Declaration of Helsinki）」，說明了受試者有絕對的權利了解實驗內容，保障了受試者「知情同意」的權益。數十年的努力之下，美國和其他國家都誓言杜絕非人道的臨床實驗，全世界都認為這種惡魔般的人體實驗不會再出現了&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qp60jU2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqp60jU2.png&h=0f218e09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/62254048_1233250940184671_5825174709460795392_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=af8a127ef43e169c16b9bc1668a17909&amp;oe=5D8A89DA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F62254048_1233250940184671_5825174709460795392_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3Daf8a127ef43e169c16b9bc1668a17909%26oe%3D5D8A89DA&h=582c6bc5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"174c5bc32e5aac4649acbba5828950cf4fb4b564","tid":1227134,"uid":44766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:37:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0606fb3085bf322df843d701c7c8a6d35f56251a","tid":1227134,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:37:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"373314cc365433648dff5170bd940cf73b1fd30d","tid":1227134,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:38:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab60aff57470e404c420089555394ade8c38a3c9","tid":1227134,"uid":25001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:38:20.000Z","msg":"快啲推上熱門"},{"pid":"b9e649953f5d89f3b963f8d4373471e8aa234a79","tid":1227134,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"460cddf190efb67cb3585166d707c713e52fe3ad","tid":1227134,"uid":50776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20