":"推"},{"pid":"ecd96c9a5932de3bbd8d3a7b1fe4dade01f188a5","tid":1227134,"uid":116503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de33dcfe94ef3cac6a42b97a6abc49f4da8fd199","tid":1227134,"uid":121387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:56:44.000Z","msg":"好感動"},{"pid":"cf70495082e6f86016be249a7ddee9b340854d91","tid":1227134,"uid":223455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:02:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"34cba059086e3a5b37264a6579b7390514831dc4","tid":1227134,"uid":148607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"797d4ecb9532c94a1699aa9ffb3a9b3452229938","tid":1227134,"uid":25001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:34:01.000Z","msg":"阻你一陣<br />\n<br />\n我們連續幾天的抗爭仍未得到正當回應<br />\n警察和政府的不合理對待使全世界嘩然<br />\n但即使採用任何手段 也不能令香港人滅聲<br />\n香港全民歸位<br />\n不甘示弱 只為明天<br />\n6.16 不見不散<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以用少少時間睇段片 我地中學生用左一晚時間剪片<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Share 出去<br />\n我地一日不撤回 一日不散去<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rpjIPEuHtLw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrpjIPEuHtLw&d=1pbl5WvK8XMTdm%2FDcZs%2FeHljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=077d40dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rpjIPEuHtLw</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:02:37.000Z","msg":"睇完又不斷回想起出黎嗰幾日嘅記憶。<br />\n69嗰日由遊行到留守到凌晨三點幾，<br />\n611夜晚收工後去到添馬，瞓唔安，坐唔落。<br />\n612一齊塞住馬路，回想起每個畫面真係好感動<br />\n同時亦都好無奈。好多好多都係20幾歲嘅學生，<br />\n我哋學生為咗自己，為咗住係香港嘅港豬，為咗住係香港嘅某啲廢老，到底付出咗幾多？<br />\n深信有付出過嘅大家，銘記在心"},{"pid":"0c07971f72a935971d540d909bd72288e0284f68","tid":1227134,"uid":231007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:08:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4455d95d6bb49857c095d7cc46c99ba3ab68e3d","tid":1227134,"uid":207942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:08:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c76379538ade6d267053d9cd8deb24948df526c","tid":1227134,"uid":112701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:09:13.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}